                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "line_text": "Enfant, je croyais que la vie",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Était un beau rêve des cieux !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Lorsque tes chants mélodieux\nFrappaient mon oreille ravie,\nEnfant, je croyais que la vie\nÉtait un beau rêve des cieux !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Ta voix dissipait ma souffrance,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Elle faisait rêver mon cœur,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Et ce rêve était le bonheur,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Ce bonheur était l'espérance !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ta voix dissipait ma souffrance,\nElle faisait rêver mon cœur,\nEt ce rêve était le bonheur,\nCe bonheur était l'espérance !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Je t'écoutais en récitant,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Tout bas, une douce louange,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Puis croyant à la voix d'un ange,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Je t'adorais en t'écoutant !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Je t'écoutais en récitant,\nTout bas, une douce louange,\nPuis croyant à la voix d'un ange,\nJe t'adorais en t'écoutant !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Et je te disais : chante encore,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Chante ! que la joie ait son tour ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Si ma vie, hélas, est d'un jour ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Jusqu'au soir prolonge l'aurore !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Et je te disais : chante encore,\nChante ! que la joie ait son tour ;\nSi ma vie, hélas, est d'un jour ;\nJusqu'au soir prolonge l'aurore !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "A tes chants ma douleur s'endort,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Et lorsque leur doux bruit s'achève,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Il recommence dans mon rêve,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Ineffable et céleste accord !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "A tes chants ma douleur s'endort,\nEt lorsque leur doux bruit s'achève,\nIl recommence dans mon rêve,\nIneffable et céleste accord !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Mais loin de nous tu t'es enfuie !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Maintenant tout n'est que douleurs ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Avec l'absence sont les pleurs,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Les pleurs que nulle main n'essuie !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Mais loin de nous tu t'es enfuie !\nMaintenant tout n'est que douleurs ;\nAvec l'absence sont les pleurs,\nLes pleurs que nulle main n'essuie !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Et tout est triste devant moi !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Mon âme sanglote à toute heure…,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Je te cherche dans ma demeure,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Toujours toute pleine de toi !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Et tout est triste devant moi !\nMon âme sanglote à toute heure…,\nJe te cherche dans ma demeure,\nToujours toute pleine de toi !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Reviens, reviens, ô jeune fille !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Car moi je pleure et j'ai vingt ans !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "Et je vois le soleil qui brille,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Baiser les roses du printemps !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Reviens, reviens, ô jeune fille !\nCar moi je pleure et j'ai vingt ans !\nEt je vois le soleil qui brille,\nBaiser les roses du printemps !"
        }
